{"tid":236851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日吹緊正北風，點睇天文台報吹微風","createTime":"2017-05-10T04:21:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T10:43:06.000Z","uid":82929,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8c778b55f4d737d09f09eefd2ee6145c8a677d56","tid":236851,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T04:21:22.000Z","msg":"天天台數據就正北風，天氣描述就話吹微風<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 夏天吹西南風，天文台會講香港受到西南氣流影響，天氣不穩定<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冬天吹東北風，天文台會講香港受到東北季後風/一般偏東氣流影響，天氣寒冷/有霧<br />\n<br />\n但吹弱北風，天文台就政治正確咁話香港吹微風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n👍🏻天文台立場正確，冇維穩成份<br />\n<br />\n👎🏻天文台幫大陸維穩"},{"pid":"608e6f95124cf72e25d53d018cc338cd0cd927cc","tid":236851,"uid":45840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T04:26:44.000Z","msg":"係真係微風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4ee125069d518c22133164f0fff54807a3cbe9a","tid":236851,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T04:28:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲未計天文台d預測<br />\n早3日d預測都失敗，預測有雨就變晴天，預測冇雨就變狂風大雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇住個雷達黎做落大雨預警，搵個連登仔都識啦<br />\n<br />\n天文台都唔知搞乜，年年都呃經費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"204bccad3a3851c4374cdb67db4b59a6eeff5d52","tid":236851,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T04:28:39.000Z","msg":"天文台幾時都係幫港共維穩架啦<br />\n<br />\n睇下之前紅黑雨 3號8號波就知"},{